         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 3 of Imperator Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius, Pachon 15 for the arithmesis of Phamenoth. Paid by Kronion son of Kronion son of Pakebkis, his mother being Sarap( ) as poll-tax of the third year in the Linypheia district twenty drachmas, that is, 20, with additional payments of ten bronze obols.</ab>
